Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:06.36,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,They're nothing compared to \Nthe spirit of justice that's here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:10.86,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's definitely here! \NThere's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.86,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Compared to that spirit, you're nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:22.58,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I-I'm dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.42,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This... is just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:28.84,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,To be cornered like this with nowhere to hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:31.42,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This {\i1}must{\i0} be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.43,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You ain't got nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:37.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...left to run away to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:38.97,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.56,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,J-Josuke looks really hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.73,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,While we were waiting, \Nit seems the battle had already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:47.98,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.82,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...that's Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.90,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Someone is injured over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:55.74,Secondary,Guy,0,0,0,,Stand back! There's a gas leak that could cause an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.28,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Bring the ambulance over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.12,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Get me a stretcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:58.07,Secondary,Guy,0,0,0,,This area is dangerous, so please stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.37,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:00:59.58,Secondary,Guy,0,0,0,,Stand all the way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.95,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Can you hear me? An ambulance is on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:03.12,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,You're going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.37,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Don't let her get near Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.17,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,We'll have you in the hospital and being treated in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.09,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:14.26,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,You'll be fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.80,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.56,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He turned that lady into a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.31,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,How many fingers am I holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:30.48,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro, you'll have to use Star Platinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.69,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.90,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,But it won't help us unless I get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:38.91,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Even if I stopped time, I'm too far away to do anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.91,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I need to be at least five meters closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:45.12,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,So you've resorted to taking someone hostage and turning them into a bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:50.17,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Just try me! I'll heal her up in a heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:54.01,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,No! This isn't as simple as him taking a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:56.97,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He has a hidden ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:01.35,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's called Bites the Dust, and he can use it to blow away time!
Comment: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:09.69,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,513)\pos(135,890)\fs60}Episode 39: {\fs80} Farewell, Morioh: Town of Golden Hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:10.56,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}I bet it only works on people who aren't Stand users, like me and that lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:16.57,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,...and only when Kira is \Nbacked into a corner with no way to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:24.45,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Basically, when he feels completely hopeless, his ability activates and he can turn people into a bomb that will let him go an hour back in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.45,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:34.09,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The knuckles and skin on your hand are so soft and smooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.38,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You have such attractive, fair fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:39.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Please, will you rub my cheek?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.59,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:44.85,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Having my cheek rubbed is so calming...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.98,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,When I was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.27,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You've heard of Leonardo da Vinci's Mona Lisa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.49,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The first time I saw that painting in an art book...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:03.24,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,When I first saw it... How can I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.95,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This is a bit unseemly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.50,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...I had a throbbing erection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:15.25,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I specifically cut out the portion of the picture with her hands and hung it in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:18.26,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I would like to cut off your hands, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.09,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.18,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My name is Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:29.85,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I've killed forty-eight women with beautiful hands thus far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.35,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You're the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:35.11,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You're the only one who will know my identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad! Bites the Dust is about to activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:46.99,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,If we don't defeat him right now, \Neveryone but that lady will be blown up and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.66,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.67,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Coming for me, Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:04:00.30,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I gained the ability of Bites the Dust\Nprecisely so I would never have to directly fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Approach me, if you dare! \NJust try and stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.14,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,How long are you able to stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.56,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Go ahead and push me even further into a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:13.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Bringing me to my limit will make Bites the Dust appear again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro, stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.77,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You can't let him trigger Killer Queen's switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.49,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.41,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm at my limit! I'm going to trigger it! {This and the next line are the same as line 116/117}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.66,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:37.34,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I-I did it! It activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.16,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I've returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.04,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It worked once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.54,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Bites the Dust pulled through for me once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I've finally defeated them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.55,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,From now on, I'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.77,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.98,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The birds came from behind me, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.23,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:44.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, this isn't the usual route I take to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:50.83,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If Bites the Dust had succeeded in turning back time an hour, I would be on my way to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.37,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:58.33,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That's right. I forgot I had put my wristwatch in my breast pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.67,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Why is it broken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.96,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It should be 8:29!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.38,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Bites the Dust should have taken effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:13.01,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This watch Hayato broke using Stray Cat\N should have returned to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.68,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Don't you realize what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:24.28,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,So that man in the photo Rohan took \Nnamed Kawajiri Kosaku really was Kira Yoshikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:27.49,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,This is finally over now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:32.91,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,After all this time, they finally cornered you, Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.08,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,And just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.54,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.67,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I suppose that isn't a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.08,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,You encountered me fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.01,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Something very traumatic must have happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:50.34,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Something so traumatic that it \Nmade you forget what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Are you a new Stand user?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:57.14,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,You don't understand! You've died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.81,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.11,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,This isn't a Stand ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:15.62,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,This is proof that all that remains of you is the tainted black soul of a serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:21.58,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Well? Now do you remember how you died?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.92,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If I stop time now, I still won't be close enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You can't let him trigger the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.93,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm at my limit! I'm going to trigger it! {This and the next line are the same as line 78/79}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:31.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.85,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Act 3! 3 Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.89,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,He is now within five meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,S-H-I-T!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.87,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You fucking pieces of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.24,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Star Platinum! The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:08.71,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Koichi, you really are a guy I can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:13.22,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'm glad I came to this town and met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.59,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.97,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.43,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.48,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:38.78,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.58,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Resume time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,H-He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.38,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.43,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'll trigger it... I'm gonna trigger it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:08.02,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm going to... activate Bites the Dust... once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:11.53,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Wh-What happened? \NHe suddenly flew backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:16.24,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do it... I-I'm really gonna do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:20.62,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm... gonna trigger... the switch now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.20,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I know he's our enemy, but this is appalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.71,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.46,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.55,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There's someone on the ground behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:49.31,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-This is terrible!\N This man was run over by an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.98,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I didn't realize he was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.94,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Forward! Drive forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.82,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All of you! Get outside of the tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.99,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Get back! Get back immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.82,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Were you injured, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:07.41,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's too late. He's dead. Died on impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.13,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.01,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's like he intentionally dove under the tire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.88,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:22.14,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to make any excuses, \Nbut I didn't have a chance to restrain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.14,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.73,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,His head was crushed between the tire and the pavement...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.14,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The skin on his face tore clean off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.65,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.40,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Do you happen to know the identity of the deceased?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:37.15,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,He told me his name was Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.49,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.83,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There's a family by the name of Kira\N in Kotodai who go back generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.95,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I heard the only living member lives alone, so he may not have any family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.96,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,An accident... \NHe was killed by complete accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.96,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,This is a fitting end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.25,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,The legal system wouldn't have been\N capable of properly punishing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.72,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,This is the best we could have asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:03.47,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I... I never really got along with my Papa very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.06,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,But that man... He murdered him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.48,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I wanted him to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.77,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I wanted anyone who could punish him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.37,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,You seem to remember now, Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.99,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,You remember how you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.70,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I can tell you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.83,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who{\i0} the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:39.21,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago, you didn't have a Stand ability, so you couldn't make corpses disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:42.97,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,That's why, when I died, it made major news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.72,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Do you remember the wound \Nyou gave me on my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:54.61,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Or perhaps you don't remember since it was \Nyour first murder and you forgot to take my hand with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.36,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.61,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Your name is... Sugimoto Reimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:05.66,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Why have you been waiting here for fifteen years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:14.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Why would you go to the trouble of showing me \Nthe wound on your back and telling me who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:19.96,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This wouldn't happen to be the place where you're not supposed to turn around, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:28.06,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My father once told me there was a road \Nin this town where the spirits of the dead roam...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:31.93,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...and that if you ever found yourself there, \Nyou should {\i1}never{\i0} turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:38.23,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If you were to turn around, \Nan unstoppable power would drag you off somewhere. {"you" to be consistent with the lines before and after this}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:46.91,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You weren't trying to force me to turn around \Nby showing me the wound on your back, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:52.29,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You wouldn't ever consider deceiving me like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.79,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I'll have you turn around instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.79,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Hmm? I'm curious to see what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.34,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Come on! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:08.22,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Do you really think I wasn't \Nexpecting you to pull a stunt like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:13.73,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,We've waited here for\N fifteen years for you to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.73,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,We?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.77,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Arnold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:32.70,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,The time of your punishment is at hand, Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.66,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What? What are these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.54,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Make these things explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.51,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:50.39,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Wh-Where are these things going to take me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.64,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.77,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.98,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,...I'm sure it's a place where you'll {\i1}never{\i0} rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.08,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,At long last...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.92,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,...we can finally go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.13,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,The two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.39,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Reimi! Are you really leaving for good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:40.44,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It would be okay if you stayed\N for a little bit longer, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It feels like our town is losing its guardian angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:47.03,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I feel anxious knowing you're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:52.28,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Thank you! But we have no business\N left to take care of in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.08,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,The time has come for us to leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.70,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:02.42,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,What about you, Rohan? \NAre you going to miss me and cry once I'm gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.92,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.30,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Why would I ever miss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.72,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,You already died fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:20.39,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I've said it before, but I firmly believe you ghosts would find more relief by not clinging to earthly attachments and passing on from this world. {This line is a reference to line 211 in episode 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:32.20,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Oh, fine! \NSince this is the last time I'll see you, I'll be honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.20,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'm going to miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.91,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I don't want you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.17,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.75,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Josuke! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.09,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,It's finally over, Reimi! {As if Yukako did fucking anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.13,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Yukako! Hazamada, and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.84,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,We have arrived to see you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.51,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This is kinda weird to say \Nto a dead person, but take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.40,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I'm gonna miss ya, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.86,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You're a wonderful young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.29,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Reimi! Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.25,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,This town is finally safe thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.04,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Thank you, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:26.63,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,But in my heart, \NI believe it was all of us who saved Morioh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:32.51,Main,Joseke,0,0,0,,I promise nobody here will ever forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.18,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.01,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Goodbye, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.31,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Reimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.78,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.04,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,He's awfully late tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.25,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Must be overtime at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.54,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,He could have called, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.79,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:12.17,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.68,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,I'll eat once Papa gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.85,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.68,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'll wait for him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.31,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Once Papa is home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.73,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,...I'll eat with you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.11,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:37.74,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,By the way, have you gotten a bit taller recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:43.37,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Our town, Morioh, was deeply hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:48.79,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,It was hurt by the monster it spawned named Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:53.38,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hayato's mom will wait forever for her husband to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:58.76,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Shigechi's parents will also wait forever for him to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:06.52,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,The families who had daughters and sisters killed \Nby Kira Yoshikage will forever await their return, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:11.27,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,The pain from their wounds will only ever grow deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.99,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,How can we possibly ease their suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:21.91,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Will their pain threaten the future of this town, \Nor will it eventually fade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.99,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,I honestly don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.00,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Are you worried, Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.67,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,About leaving this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.84,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Yeah, a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:41.18,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,After watching Josuke and the others become involved in \Nthis incident in Morioh, I can only come to one conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:47.81,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The young people in this town have golden spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:56.61,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The same golden spirits shining with justice\Nas those we met on our journey to Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.91,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I see it in Josuke and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.08,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,They'll be fine if they cling tightly to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.50,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We'll never have to worry about the safety of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.29,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.92,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:16.88,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I should say goodbye\N to the son I'm so proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:20.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That photo I gave you of my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You still got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:26.81,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Of course! \NPut it right in my wallet, just like you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:31.73,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Although I'm leaving without seeing her,\N I wish her nothing but happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:35.94,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,So, you really did put it in your wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I've got the edge of that photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Crazy Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'll be taking this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:51.33,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,A good dad should give his son an allowance anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:57.75,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If I let you take that photo home with you,\N your old lady would just get pissed at you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.75,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,{\an8}Y-You little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:03.30,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gonna take back what you said \Nabout his golden spirit, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:18.69,Narrator,Koichi,0,0,0,,The invisible baby's mother was never found, \Nso Mr. Joseph Joestar ended up adopting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:28.03,Narrator,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Kujo Jotaro received his doctorate from a thesis he wrote\N about the starfish population on the beach here in Morioh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.20,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Josuke, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.37,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,You ate the snack I was saving for myself {\i1}again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.50,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.50,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,I'll just have to drink his juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.50,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.88,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.47,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,I was busy making us lunch and lost track of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:49.39,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? You made us lunch? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.43,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I can't wait to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.65,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:13.08,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Oh? Oh, here it comes! \NFuck yeah! It's real intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:17.50,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Maybe it'll turn ya back t'normal, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.26,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.22,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,My skin is so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.55,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,My eyes feel so clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.43,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,The food here was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:36.31,Main,Yuuya,0,0,0,,{\pos(1240,1055)}Right? I'm so much sexier than before, \NI don't even know what to do with my bad self!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.86,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Yutie-pie, you're glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.86,Secondary,Bitches,0,0,0,,So shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.94,Main,Yuuya,0,0,0,,Hmm, think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.69,Main,Yuuya,0,0,0,,I'm glowing, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.24,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Grazie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.12,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I most patiently await your next visit.
